/-- The ordering on group topologies on the group `Œ≥`. `t ‚â§ s` if every set open in `s` is also open
in `t` (`t` is finer than `s`). -/
@[to_additive "The ordering on group topologies on the group `Œ≥`. `t ‚â§ s` if every set open in `s`
is also open in `t` (`t` is finer than `s`)."]
instance : partial_order (group_topology Œ±) :=
